title: We Talk With THE Fav Swiftie DJ, @djrog1998!
description:
You know him all over TikTok for his beautiful mashups, and Taylor Swift does too! We get to talk to DJ Rog about his favorite mixes, his impressive career and the advice that he DIDN'T take that led to him getting praise from Taylor!
Check him out on TikTok, @djrog1998! And hopefully, we will be catching him live soon!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Please let us know!
